Use virtualenv with python3
$ virtualenv -p /usr/bin/python3 venv
$ source venv/bin/activate

Install the requirements
$ pip install -r requirements.txt

To run using gunicorn
$ gunicorn --bind 0.0.0.0:8002 clever_red.wsgi:application

The production settings uses environment variables
$ export STATIC_URL=''
$ export MEDIA_URL=''
$ export WORK_DATABASE

The static folder contains the media folder

